Pager

Version 1.1 for FWF V4.0

N.B.	The widget files are computer-generated. The real source is
	*.w. It has been processed with Wbuild (available by anonymous
	FTP from ftp.let.rug.nl in the same directory
	as the FWF sources.)

Author:	Bert Bos <bert@let.rug.nl>
	Alfa-informatica, Rijksuniversiteit Groningen, The Netherlands

History
1.0	April 1993
1.0.1	Replaced ltoa() with sprintf(), which seems more portable
1.1	[Dec 93] Removed italic/bold font handling (must wait for a later time)
1.2	(12 Feb '96) background_pixel replaced by background (see Common)

